  mutalist_cernos: "On hit: Arrows spawn a 2.5m Toxin cloud dealing damage over time for 10 seconds, with a chance to apply a Toxin proc every second. Clouds alert enemies despite the weapon being silent. On kill: Ragdolls targets; bodies follow the projectile, damaging enemies in their path and pinning corpses to walls.",
