  onos: "[Incarnon] Landing 12 weakpoint hits fully charges the Transmutation gauge. Alt-fire: Transforms into an Arm Cannon firing a wide Radiation beam that narrows. Fully charging the shot releases a Heat beam with 5m punch through that explodes in a 3m radius (penetrates walls). Features a unique magazine up to 350 rounds. |} |-|Melee= No documented Melee Incarnon passives. </tabber> </div> {{!-!}}Unregistered= <div class=\"tabber-borderless\"> <table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%\"> <tr> <th style=\"width:15%\">Main Category</th> <th style=\"width:85%\">Subcategories with No Documented Passives</th> </tr> <tr> <td>Other</td> <td>Archwing • Companion • Modular • Railjack </td> </tr> </table> </div> }}</div> {{clr}} == Passive Archetypes == {| class=\"wikitable\"",
