  prisma_twin_gremlins: "On kill: Ragdolls targets; bodies follow the projectile, damaging enemies in their path and pinning corpses to walls. |} |-|Dual Shotguns= {| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%\" ! style=\"width:20%\" | Weapon ! style=\"width:80%\" | Passive",
